Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1000
Set Height 550
Set Theme "ayu"

Show
Sleep 1s
Type "ndoc fs"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
Down
Sleep 200ms
Down
Sleep 200ms
Down
Sleep 200ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Type "q"
Sleep 1s
Type "ndoc fs.readFile"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "q"
Sleep 1s
